0:11:06.16,000 --> 0:11:1,000
Well let's take a look. Let's take a look at the Great Depression.

233
0:11:10.16,000 --> 0:11:12,000
Here is GDP per capita

234
0:11:12.16,000 --> 0:11:15,000
from 1900 to 1929.

235
0:11:15.16,000 --> 0:11:19,000
Now let's imagine that you were an economist in 1929,

236
0:11:19.16,000 --> 0:11:22,000
